title: Tanya's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, All Raw
description: Living cuisine/raw food restaurant and beverage bar in Chelsea since 2014. Drinks lists includes juices, coffee with hazelnut milk, superfood packed cocktails. Serves plant-based burgers, raw chocolate cake, cashew cheese platter. Kitchen uses seasonal produce. Natural atmosphere. Vegan except for bee products in some items.
